<% if @group_invitation.recipient_profile %>
  <p>Hi <%= @group_invitation.recipient.first_name %>,</p>
<% else %>
  <p>Hi there,</p>
<% end %>
<p><%= @group_invitation.sender.full_name %> has invited you to join <%= @group_invitation.group_invitable.product.name %> as a referencer. With this you can help them by verifying that you are using the product and by writing customer review.</p>

<p>You can accept the invitation on the <%= link_to "product customer page", product_product_customer_url(@group_invitation.group_invitable.product, @group_invitation.group_invitable) %>.</p>

<p>Cheers,<br />Faskyn Team</p>